description: "Query: clickbench_q23"
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |   Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |     Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, min(hits.URL), min(hits.Title), count(Int64(1)) AS c, count(DISTINCT hits.UserID)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.SearchPhrase]], aggr=[[min(hits.URL), min(hits.Title), count(Int64(1)), count(DISTINCT hits.UserID)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[Title, UserID, URL, SearchPhrase], full_filters=[hits.Title LIKE Utf8("%Google%"), hits.URL NOT LIKE Utf8("%.google.%"), hits.SearchPhrase != Utf8("")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=postgres compute_context=host=Tcp("benchmarking-postgres-rw.dataplatform.svc.cluster.local"),port=5432,db=clickbench_accelerated,user=postgres, initial_sql=SELECT "hits"."SearchPhrase", min("hits"."URL"), min("hits"."Title"), count(1) AS "c", count(DISTINCT "hits"."UserID") FROM "hits" WHERE (("hits"."Title" LIKE '%Google%' AND "hits"."URL" NOT LIKE '%.google.%') AND ("hits"."SearchPhrase" <> '')) GROUP BY "hits"."SearchPhrase" ORDER BY "c" DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
